### SUMMARY TABLE

| Aspect | Implementation |
|--------|-----------------|
| **Entry Point** | `/src/main.tsx` with RouterProvider |
| **Routing** | TanStack Router with file-based routes in `/src/routes/` |
| **State Management** | Zustand stores (preferential) + TanStack Query (server state) |
| **Context/Providers** | Limited React Context; primarily Zustand + Query + custom providers |
| **Styling System** | Tailwind CSS 4 + CSS custom properties + CVA |
| **Component Library** | BaseUI React (headless) + custom shadcn-style components |
| **Theme Support** | useTheme hook with system, light, dark modes; stored in localStorage |
| **Local Storage** | 5 main keys for state, theme, drafts, terminal, settings |
| **TypeScript** | Strict; uses Effect Schema for runtime validation |
| **Build Tool** | Vite 8 with React 19 compiler plugin |
| **Testing** | Vitest with collocated .test.ts files |

