1. **App loads** -> `useTheme.ts` module executes at import time -> reads `t3code:color-theme` from localStorage -> resolves to a `ThemeDefinition` from `@t3tools/shared/themes` -> calls `applyTheme()` which (a) toggles `.dark` class on `<html>` based on `isDark`, (b) sets all CSS custom properties on `document.documentElement.style`.

